Miscellaneous Highlights: The Suns lost to the Lakers and there was plenty to learn from.
The final preseason game was the dress rehearsal for the start of the regular season.
The Suns face the Lakers in preseason, and Anthony Davis dominates Nurkic.
This was a “welcome to the NBA, rookie” moment for Dunn.
Beal shot just 4-of-15 from the field, went 1-of-6 from deep, and posted a -10 in the +/-.
Others: Kevin Durant played 31 minutes, Beal played 30, and Booke logged 28.
The Suns will head to the City of Angels, where they’ll kick off their campaign against the Clippers.
Just two days later, they’ll face the Lakers again.
